data.description:
Discover the perfect blend of space and style in this delightful 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home. Nestled in the heart of Tulia, Tx, this home offers a comfortable and convenient lifestyle for you and your family.
4 bedrooms for ample space and versatility
3 well-appointed bathrooms for your comfort and convenience. 2 inviting living areas to accommodate your lifestyle kitchen with all the essentials. Finished Basement
Cozy backyard for outdoor relaxation, flexible layout, ideal for families seeking room to grow and entertain. The light filled living spaces create a warm and welcoming atmosphere, while the backyard provides a private retreat for outdoor enjoyment.

Located in a quiet, family-friendly neighborhood, you'll enjoy easy access to local schools, parks, shops, and more.
